### 4. RAG didático — pergunta única.
### Pré-req: rodar `3-index.rest` uma vez.
### JSON é o default. Use `?format=markdown` para a versão renderizada.

@host = http://localhost:8000


### 4.1 — `openai` · pergunta clássica sobre IRA.
POST {{host}}/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What is the difference between a Roth IRA and a Traditional IRA?",
  "embedder": "openai",
  "top_k": 5
}


### 4.2 — `bge-small` · juros compostos (top_k menor).
POST {{host}}/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "How does compound interest work?",
  "embedder": "bge-small",
  "top_k": 3
}


### 4.3 — `bge-large` · advisor + mortgage (pergunta mais ambígua).
POST {{host}}/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Do financial advisors get better deals on mortgages?",
  "embedder": "bge-large",
  "top_k": 5
}


### 4.4 — `openai` · pergunta FORA do corpus.
POST {{host}}/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What is the current Bitcoin price?",
  "embedder": "openai",
  "top_k": 5
}


### 4.5 — `bge-small` · sem o controle (só RAG).
POST {{host}}/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "How does compound interest work?",
  "embedder": "bge-small",
  "top_k": 3,
  "with_control": false
}


### 4.6 — `bge-large` · markdown human-readable (`?format=markdown`).
POST {{host}}/ask?format=markdown
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "How does compound interest work?",
  "embedder": "bge-large",
  "top_k": 3
}
